    "title": "FR: enforce clang-format on all source files in CI",
    "body": "Bitcoin uses [clang-format](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/src/.clang-format) but it is not enforced by automatic tools, so we can see that some files are not formatted according to current `.clang-format` standard.\r\n\r\nThis FR is also a request to format all source files according to `.clang-format`.",
